<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<workout_file>
  <author>Gravel God Training</author>
  <name>W01_Thu_Aug20_Anaerobic_Test</name>
  <description>[HIGH FUEL: Target 60-90g carbs/hr. Eat early, eat often.]

Finisher - Week 1/12 - 12 weeks to Spirit World 100
Phase: BASE

WARM-UP:
-20min building from Z1 to Z2

MAIN SET:
-3-minute all-out test after warmup. Establishes CP and W'.
-Cadence: 100-110rpm - high turnover
-Position: Drops, aggressive

COOL-DOWN:
-10min easy spin Z1-Z2

PROGRESSION:
-Level 1/6: Introductory - Focus on form and learning the workout pattern
-3-minute all-out test - go hard from the start, hold on

PURPOSE:
Fitness assessment. Establish baseline metrics for training zones.

EXECUTION:
-Focus on consistent effort and good form throughout.

NUTRITION:
-40-60g carbs/hr for efforts over 60min.

HYDRATION:
-500-750ml/hr. Adjust for heat and humidity.</description>
  <sportType>bike</sportType>
  <workout>
    <Warmup Duration="1200" PowerLow="0.50" PowerHigh="0.75"/>
    <SteadyState Duration="1740" Power="0.55" CadenceLow="100" CadenceHigh="110"/>
    <FreeRide Duration="180" FlatRoad="1"/>
    <Cooldown Duration="600" PowerLow="0.75" PowerHigh="0.50"/>
  </workout>
</workout_file>